N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 94.3 - Photographic record of readings

State Regulations

Subsequent to January 1, 1952 electric corporations shall
maintain a photographic record of all readings taken from indicating types of
demand meters and registers used to measure alternating current
service. Notes
